1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,640
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 33=

3
00:00:44,541 --> 00:00:45,291
I don't want you to go!

4
00:00:47,708 --> 00:00:49,291
Don't push me too far.

5
00:00:53,958 --> 00:00:55,416
After everything we have been through,

6
00:00:56,916 --> 00:00:58,416
we finally found our way to each other.

7
00:01:01,583 --> 00:01:02,583
Why leave now?

8
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:06,916
Because today I learned

9
00:01:08,583 --> 00:01:10,291
that the truth I spent so long chasing,

10
00:01:11,541 --> 00:01:12,583
the true culprit behind it all,

11
00:01:13,416 --> 00:01:14,125
was my father.

12
00:01:14,125 --> 00:01:15,208
So what?

13
00:01:16,625 --> 00:01:17,583
That was your father,

14
00:01:17,916 --> 00:01:18,791
not you.

15
00:01:18,875 --> 00:01:20,083
But I cannot accept it.

16
00:01:21,666 --> 00:01:23,500
I'm selfish, cowardly, and weak.

17
00:01:24,958 --> 00:01:25,625
Young Duke.

18
00:01:27,666 --> 00:01:28,750
You come from a noble house.

19
00:01:29,916 --> 00:01:30,916
You are in the prime of your life.

20
00:01:32,583 --> 00:01:33,291
Without me,

21
00:01:34,416 --> 00:01:35,791
you can have someone far better.

22
00:01:37,416 --> 00:01:37,958
There is no one better.

23
00:01:40,583 --> 00:01:41,583
Every other woman

24
00:01:43,750 --> 00:01:45,625
is nothing but dust to me.

25
00:01:48,583 --> 00:01:49,250
One day,

26
00:01:51,583 --> 00:01:53,750
you will regret saying that.

27
00:01:58,500 --> 00:01:59,125
Never.

28
00:02:01,958 --> 00:02:02,500
Bingfan.

29
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:05,625
If one day,

30
00:02:07,375 --> 00:02:08,750
I regret even half a word

31
00:02:09,041 --> 00:02:10,125
of what I said today,

32
00:02:13,583 --> 00:02:15,041
may I die under a hail of arrows,

33
00:02:16,916 --> 00:02:18,083
with no body left whole.

34
00:02:19,208 --> 00:02:19,958
Don't say that.

35
00:02:20,458 --> 00:02:21,291
I won't thank you for it.

36
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:27,140
♪I whisper in my heart♪

37
00:02:31,125 --> 00:02:32,291
I will go with you!

38
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:38,060
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

39
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:40,890
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

40
00:02:41,333 --> 00:02:41,833
What did you say?

41
00:02:42,875 --> 00:02:43,875
I will go with you.

42
00:02:46,208 --> 00:02:47,375
Young Duke,

43
00:02:48,541 --> 00:02:49,583
young lord,

44
00:02:50,875 --> 00:02:51,833
none of them matter to me.

45
00:02:55,791 --> 00:02:56,500
Wherever you go,

46
00:02:57,541 --> 00:02:57,916
I go.

47
00:02:58,875 --> 00:02:59,666
Across the world,

48
00:02:59,916 --> 00:03:00,541
through all its beauty,

49
00:03:05,375 --> 00:03:06,541
having you is enough.

50
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:10,060
♪This longing I cannot say♪

51
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:15,390
♪I wish you could hear♪

52
00:03:38,333 --> 00:03:38,958
What is this place?

53
00:03:39,875 --> 00:03:40,750
Where it all began.

54
00:03:43,083 --> 00:03:43,500
Father.

55
00:03:44,583 --> 00:03:45,708
Was Wang Yan's testimony

56
00:03:46,583 --> 00:03:48,208
truly what happened back then?

57
00:03:49,375 --> 00:03:50,625
Were you really one of Prince Fu's men?

58
00:03:51,708 --> 00:03:53,000
Did you really lose all sense
of right and wrong

59
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:54,375
just to protect him?

60
00:03:55,583 --> 00:03:56,875
You were the one who taught me

61
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,625
to know right

62
00:03:58,625 --> 00:04:00,666
(Grave of My Late Parents)
from wrong.

63
00:04:01,333 --> 00:04:02,541
Why would you do that?

64
00:04:04,291 --> 00:04:06,625
Why would you betray the faith
I had in you?

65
00:04:06,625 --> 00:04:08,140
(Grave of My Late Parents)

66
00:04:14,541 --> 00:04:16,583
I think

67
00:04:18,583 --> 00:04:19,583
we will be staying here for a while.

68
00:04:21,083 --> 00:04:21,708
We?

69
00:04:28,416 --> 00:04:28,666
We.

70
00:04:31,708 --> 00:04:32,291
We.

71
00:04:32,291 --> 00:04:35,270
♪Through wind and rain, I will follow♪

72
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:37,680
♪With no regret♪

73
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:42,680
♪For you, I will guard
what is precious with all my heart♪

74
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,560
♪Even if memories burn to ash♪

75
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:48,020
♪I will never forget♪

76
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:52,060
♪Even if the past was only a dream♪

77
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,180
(Northern Bureau)

78
00:04:57,833 --> 00:04:58,250
My lord.

79
00:04:58,916 --> 00:04:59,875
Bad news.

80
00:05:00,416 --> 00:05:02,625
Her Ladyship has stormed
into the Northern Bureau.

81
00:05:03,041 --> 00:05:03,750
Zhang Weimin!

82
00:05:08,583 --> 00:05:09,666
Your Ladyship.

83
00:05:09,916 --> 00:05:11,291
Forgive me for not greeting you sooner.

84
00:05:11,541 --> 00:05:13,416
Your female Jinyiwei stole my son away.

85
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:15,208
I'm here to demand him back.

86
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:19,041
You have ten days.

87
00:05:19,583 --> 00:05:20,208
If my son Beiming

88
00:05:20,541 --> 00:05:22,458
is found within ten days,
I will let this go.

89
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,500
If not,

90
00:05:24,166 --> 00:05:25,250
Duke Zheng will submit a memorial

91
00:05:25,958 --> 00:05:26,916
straight to His Majesty.

92
00:05:27,541 --> 00:05:28,125
And none of you

93
00:05:28,458 --> 00:05:29,833
will get away with this.

94
00:05:31,041 --> 00:05:31,541
Yes.

95
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:32,583
Hua.

96
00:05:33,375 --> 00:05:35,916
Bingfan and Young Master Chang
must be where it all began.

97
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:37,750
Go find Bingfan.

98
00:05:38,125 --> 00:05:39,333
I respect her choice.

99
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:42,166
Well?

100
00:05:43,208 --> 00:05:44,166
Does it feel like home?

101
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:48,208
Beiming, you are back.

102
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:53,666
You really plan to live here?

103
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,708
Bingfan.

104
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,500
Where is the bounty hunter

105
00:06:03,833 --> 00:06:06,666
who once swore she would never
turn back?

106
00:06:07,208 --> 00:06:08,791
You were the one who told me
not to give up.

107
00:06:09,666 --> 00:06:11,583
We became sisters, bound by life
and death.

108
00:06:12,041 --> 00:06:13,666
And now you are abandoning us.

109
00:06:14,416 --> 00:06:15,375
I don't care what your reason is.

110
00:06:16,208 --> 00:06:17,333
I will look down on you for this.

111
00:06:21,250 --> 00:06:22,625
(Can I really leave everything behind?)

112
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,625
(Can I keep this man
who loves me so deeply)

113
00:06:26,125 --> 00:06:28,333
(tied to me and ruin his life?)

114
00:06:29,875 --> 00:06:30,625
(Shen Bingfan.)

115
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,541
(When did you become so selfish?)

116
00:06:44,041 --> 00:06:45,083
Your skills have slipped.

117
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:50,500
Why did you ambush me?

118
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:52,500
I won't watch you give up on yourself

119
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:53,958
and be like this.

120
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:56,000
So you followed me

121
00:06:56,791 --> 00:06:57,958
just to talk me into going back.

122
00:06:59,791 --> 00:07:01,500
I said I would always protect you.

123
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:03,083
I won't break that promise.

124
00:07:37,416 --> 00:07:39,083
(In the world of the Jinyiwei,)

125
00:07:39,625 --> 00:07:41,208
(there is only execution,)

126
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,500
(not questions.)

127
00:07:42,791 --> 00:07:43,833
(There is only life and death,)

128
00:07:44,041 --> 00:07:44,916
(not hesitation.)

129
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:46,125
(There is only obedience,)

130
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,541
(not defiance.)

131
00:07:48,541 --> 00:07:49,625
(Those who start and don't finish)

132
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:51,083
(shall be condemned by all.)

133
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:52,416
(Those who forget imperial grace)

134
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:54,166
(shall be condemned by all.)

135
00:07:54,583 --> 00:07:57,750
(Those who abandon right
and wrong shall be condemned by all.)

136
00:07:58,916 --> 00:08:00,291
(Those who start and don't finish)

137
00:08:00,458 --> 00:08:01,416
(shall be condemned by all.)

138
00:08:01,625 --> 00:08:02,791
(Those who forget imperial grace)

139
00:08:02,958 --> 00:08:03,875
(shall be condemned by all.)

140
00:08:04,291 --> 00:08:05,916
(Those who abandon right and wrong)

141
00:08:06,083 --> 00:08:07,083
(shall be condemned by all.)

142
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,140
(Qianhu Shen Lian, Left Qianhu Office
of the Jinyiwei)

143
00:08:08,666 --> 00:08:09,125
Father.

144
00:08:10,791 --> 00:08:12,041
No matter who you were,

145
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,041
I have joined the Jinyiwei.

146
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:16,208
From this day on,

147
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:18,666
I won't run.

148
00:08:20,208 --> 00:08:21,416
I won't fear.

149
00:08:22,708 --> 00:08:23,958
And I won't waver again.

150
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,583
(Leng Xin.)

151
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:32,500
(I'm coming.)

152
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:43,791
Hua.

153
00:08:43,916 --> 00:08:45,250
When will Bingfan come back?

154
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:49,708
Bingfan, you are finally back.

155
00:08:51,291 --> 00:08:51,958
Bingfan.

156
00:08:53,458 --> 00:08:54,833
Hua, Bingfan is back.

157
00:09:02,458 --> 00:09:04,500
Welcome back to the team,
Baihu Shen Bingfan.

158
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,470
(Baihu, Left Qianhu Office
of the Jinyiwei)

159
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:10,430
(Baihu, Left Qianhu Office
of the Jinyiwei)

160
00:09:21,875 --> 00:09:22,791
Cai Zhengbang.

161
00:09:22,833 --> 00:09:23,833
Zhou Siqi.

162
00:09:23,875 --> 00:09:24,875
Yuan Wenkang.

163
00:09:25,208 --> 00:09:27,375
They served as a Director
in the Ministry of Revenue,

164
00:09:27,375 --> 00:09:29,625
an Investigating Censor,
and a Vice Minister of Works.

165
00:09:30,125 --> 00:09:32,791
The three didn't answer to one another,

166
00:09:33,166 --> 00:09:34,583
nor did they belong to the Crown Prince
or Prince Fu.

167
00:09:35,208 --> 00:09:36,500
Why would Leng Xin kill them?

168
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:37,583
After Meizhen House was exposed,

169
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,583
a great number of officials
were implicated.

170
00:09:40,041 --> 00:09:41,833
More than a dozen were dismissed
and sent to the army.

171
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:43,125
These three

172
00:09:43,708 --> 00:09:45,000
were leading candidates

173
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,041
to replace the officials removed
above them.

174
00:09:47,583 --> 00:09:49,291
Among these vacant posts,

175
00:09:49,875 --> 00:09:51,291
which powerful office

176
00:09:51,958 --> 00:09:52,583
still has no replacement?

177
00:09:53,958 --> 00:09:55,958
The post still vacant now

178
00:09:56,291 --> 00:09:56,833
is the Right Vice Minister
at the Ministry of War.

179
00:09:58,041 --> 00:09:59,500
Who is set to fill it?

180
00:09:59,875 --> 00:10:01,833
Ding Wenyuan, formerly Assistant
Director in the Ministry of War.

181
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,833
They say

182
00:10:05,375 --> 00:10:07,500
he is a die-hard supporter
of the Crown Prince.

183
00:10:08,375 --> 00:10:09,500
Keep an eye on him,

184
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:11,416
and we will catch Leng Xin.

185
00:10:20,375 --> 00:10:20,833
What?

186
00:10:21,791 --> 00:10:23,250
You finally remembered me?

187
00:10:25,125 --> 00:10:26,416
You summoned me back for the case.

188
00:10:27,541 --> 00:10:30,958
I held a case briefing first,
then came to report.

189
00:10:31,833 --> 00:10:32,208
My lord.

190
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:34,750
My father...

191
00:10:35,416 --> 00:10:36,791
Was he really the traitor
inside the Northern Bureau?

192
00:10:39,250 --> 00:10:40,458
Your father was

193
00:10:40,958 --> 00:10:42,208
my best Jinyiwei.

194
00:10:42,583 --> 00:10:42,750
But...

195
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:43,875
Wang Yan...

196
00:10:43,958 --> 00:10:45,791
Wang Yan's words may not be true.

197
00:10:46,291 --> 00:10:47,416
If they were,

198
00:10:47,958 --> 00:10:49,583
would your father have told you,

199
00:10:50,083 --> 00:10:51,541
with his dying breath,

200
00:10:51,791 --> 00:10:53,500
to find the traitor inside the Jinyiwei?

201
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:58,791
Xintian, where are you going?

202
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,083
To catch Leng Xin.

203
00:11:01,166 --> 00:11:01,625
Xintian.

204
00:11:02,250 --> 00:11:02,958
Don't go!

205
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,750
What is wrong, Taozi?

206
00:11:06,625 --> 00:11:08,416
I heard Leng Xin is terrifying.

207
00:11:08,791 --> 00:11:09,833
Please don't go.

208
00:11:11,208 --> 00:11:13,458
Taozi, someone has to go.

209
00:11:14,041 --> 00:11:15,125
As Jinyiwei, it is my duty.

210
00:11:16,041 --> 00:11:16,666
And personally,

211
00:11:17,666 --> 00:11:18,958
Leng Xin killed Yuanrong.

212
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:20,958
Either way, I have to catch him.

213
00:11:21,416 --> 00:11:23,041
But you cannot beat him.

214
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:24,458
Taozi.

215
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:26,708
Someone still has to try.

216
00:11:28,833 --> 00:11:29,333
No!

217
00:11:30,666 --> 00:11:31,416
I cannot let you go!

218
00:11:31,875 --> 00:11:33,625
Taozi, put that down.

219
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,750
No.

220
00:11:35,541 --> 00:11:36,791
I don't want you going after Leng Xin.

221
00:11:37,166 --> 00:11:38,083
You will die.

222
00:11:38,166 --> 00:11:40,208
How can you ignore the bigger picture
like this?

223
00:11:41,875 --> 00:11:43,083
What bigger picture?

224
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:44,250
I'm not one of you.

225
00:11:45,250 --> 00:11:47,708
Taozi, why are you being so willful?

226
00:11:48,791 --> 00:11:49,833
I'm so disappointed in you.

227
00:11:53,416 --> 00:11:55,583
Then who was the traitor
my father spoke of?

228
00:11:55,875 --> 00:11:58,208
That is for you to find out.

229
00:12:00,583 --> 00:12:01,916
I need to question Wang Yan again.

230
00:12:01,916 --> 00:12:02,416
Too late.

231
00:12:03,625 --> 00:12:05,166
Wang Yan has already been executed.

232
00:12:07,083 --> 00:12:07,833
This is my fault.

233
00:12:08,125 --> 00:12:09,500
I believed his one-sided story
too easily.

234
00:12:13,541 --> 00:12:14,291
Commander.

235
00:12:14,875 --> 00:12:16,125
There is one question I wish to ask.

236
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,333
You don't have to answer.

237
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,000
My father...

238
00:12:23,375 --> 00:12:24,125
Was he

239
00:12:24,958 --> 00:12:25,500
Prince Fu's man?

240
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,125
Go do your job.

241
00:12:47,375 --> 00:12:48,458
This is good, Taozi.

242
00:13:07,291 --> 00:13:08,083
What is it, Taozi?

243
00:13:09,416 --> 00:13:10,000
Nothing.

244
00:13:21,666 --> 00:13:22,166
Taozi.

245
00:13:22,958 --> 00:13:24,541
I need to rest for a bit.

246
00:13:24,541 --> 00:13:25,916
My head hurts.

247
00:13:26,666 --> 00:13:28,666
But we have an operation tonight.

248
00:13:29,125 --> 00:13:29,791
Remember this.

249
00:13:30,291 --> 00:13:32,291
Wake me at the first watch.

250
00:13:33,333 --> 00:13:35,125
Don't forget. You must wake me.

251
00:13:43,541 --> 00:13:44,125
Watch out.

252
00:13:57,916 --> 00:13:58,541
Where is Xintian?

253
00:13:59,958 --> 00:14:01,708
Wasn't she supposed to scout ahead?

254
00:14:02,041 --> 00:14:03,416
I didn't see her when I arrived.

255
00:14:03,666 --> 00:14:04,875
I thought she was with you.

256
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:06,875
How can she be so careless?

257
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,000
Should we go back for her?

258
00:14:09,166 --> 00:14:10,083
If you go back,

259
00:14:10,125 --> 00:14:11,708
we lose another fighter.

260
00:14:14,041 --> 00:14:15,125
Forget it. We cannot wait.

261
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:17,083
We need to get inside
and protect Mr. Ding.

262
00:14:18,125 --> 00:14:18,958
Xintian...

263
00:14:19,291 --> 00:14:20,416
Gone when we need her most.

264
00:14:20,833 --> 00:14:22,083
I will beat her senseless
when we get back.

265
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:24,041
Enough. Stop complaining.

266
00:14:24,416 --> 00:14:25,125
Stick to the plan.

267
00:15:30,125 --> 00:15:31,250
Why do you keep coming at me?

268
00:16:28,708 --> 00:16:29,750
Taozi.

269
00:16:33,208 --> 00:16:34,333
What did you give me?

270
00:16:34,333 --> 00:16:35,583
Why does my head hurt so much?

271
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:44,500
What time is it?

272
00:16:46,458 --> 00:16:48,541
Just past the second watch.
Not yet the third.

273
00:16:49,625 --> 00:16:50,625
You have ruined everything.

274
00:16:55,041 --> 00:16:55,791
Xintian.

275
00:17:14,083 --> 00:17:14,666
I'm sorry.

276
00:17:14,958 --> 00:17:15,541
I'm late.

277
00:17:16,333 --> 00:17:17,125
Are you all right?

278
00:17:17,541 --> 00:17:18,666
So you remembered to show up.

279
00:17:19,291 --> 00:17:19,958
What happened to you?

280
00:17:20,375 --> 00:17:21,000
Because of you,

281
00:17:21,291 --> 00:17:22,458
we failed to close the ring.

282
00:17:22,625 --> 00:17:23,875
Young Master Chang had
to cover your position.

283
00:17:24,375 --> 00:17:25,291
With no one covering the air,

284
00:17:25,583 --> 00:17:26,583
Leng Xin found an opening.

285
00:17:26,958 --> 00:17:29,416
I only meant to sleep a little
and recover my strength.

286
00:17:31,333 --> 00:17:31,958
I'm sorry.

287
00:17:33,125 --> 00:17:34,083
What did I say?

288
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,458
She is a burden.

289
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,166
You were the one who insisted
on keeping her.

290
00:17:40,041 --> 00:17:41,375
You are not fit to be Jinyiwei.

291
00:17:45,208 --> 00:17:45,875
Bingfan.

292
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:54,375
Bingfan.

293
00:17:54,875 --> 00:17:55,958
I came to apologize.

294
00:17:56,625 --> 00:17:58,375
I don't know where your mind has been
lately,

295
00:17:58,916 --> 00:17:59,916
but it has not been on the job.

296
00:18:00,708 --> 00:18:01,541
I'm sorry.

297
00:18:01,916 --> 00:18:03,375
It won't happen again.

298
00:18:03,625 --> 00:18:05,000
I have reported this to the Commander.

299
00:18:05,375 --> 00:18:06,500
You will lose one month's pay.

300
00:18:06,916 --> 00:18:07,500
Fair enough?

301
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:08,875
Fair.

302
00:18:09,375 --> 00:18:10,250
Completely fair.

303
00:18:10,416 --> 00:18:11,166
Thank you, Bingfan.

304
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:13,000
Bingfan.

305
00:18:13,958 --> 00:18:15,708
Taozi has nowhere to go.

306
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:16,958
She has suffered enough.

307
00:18:17,541 --> 00:18:18,625
Could we let her

308
00:18:18,958 --> 00:18:20,375
stay with us for a few more days?

309
00:18:20,791 --> 00:18:21,458
Taozi?

310
00:18:21,833 --> 00:18:22,791
Send her away as soon as possible.

311
00:18:23,666 --> 00:18:25,583
She follows us every time
we are on duty.

312
00:18:25,916 --> 00:18:26,666
What is that supposed to be?

313
00:18:27,291 --> 00:18:27,708
Bingfan.

314
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:30,291
I will find somewhere for her.

315
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:31,041
Make it soon.

316
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:52,520
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

317
00:18:52,890 --> 00:18:56,270
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

318
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:59,520
♪My heart drifted lost♪

319
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:02,930
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

320
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:07,230
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

321
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:10,980
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

322
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:13,770
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

323
00:19:13,770 --> 00:19:17,810
♪I've softly let it go♪

324
00:19:17,810 --> 00:19:21,680
♪The vow you made was true♪

325
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:25,430
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

326
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,640
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

327
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:32,180
♪And forget at world's end♪

328
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,980
♪Embracing memory♪

329
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:36,350
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

330
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:40,230
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

331
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:42,560
♪I wish to let it pass♪

332
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:47,560
♪And run toward this vast life♪
